TEXT: The applicant , Mr PERSON , is a NORP national who was born in DATE and lives in GPE . He was represented before the ORG by PERSON İ. Gül , a lawyer practising in GPE . ORG ( “ the Government ” ) were represented by their Agent .
The facts of the case , as submitted by the parties , may be summarised as follows .
On DATE ORG and Highways decided to expropriate the applicant ’s land in GPE , GPE . The applicant brought an action in ORG on DATE , seeking increased compensation .

On DATE ORG awarded the applicant MONEY ( GPE ) by way of additional compensation , plus interest at the statutory rate . Both parties appealed . In the meantime the applicant initiated execution proceedings through ORG on DATE . ORG upheld the first - instance court ’s decision on DATE .
The authorities paid a total of MONEY ( TRY ) to ORG on DATE . The applicant withdrew the payment on DATE .
